WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.040
Depending on your RStudio Cloud pricing plan, you may have access to the ability to tune

00:00:07.040 --> 00:00:09.200
your project resources.

00:00:09.200 --> 00:00:14.360
To access project resources, we'll need to be within a project or an assignment on RStudio

00:00:14.360 --> 00:00:15.800
Cloud.

00:00:15.800 --> 00:00:20.280
From here, we can click on the Settings icon at the top of our project and navigate to

00:00:20.280 --> 00:00:22.240
the Resources tab.

00:00:22.240 --> 00:00:28.200
From here, we can change the amount of memory allocation, CPU allocation, and or the background

00:00:28.200 --> 00:00:30.440
execution limit.

00:00:30.440 --> 00:00:37.200
RStudio Cloud's pricing is calculated based on project hours and not project runtime.

00:00:37.200 --> 00:00:43.919
As such, note that changing our memory allocation and or changing our CPU allocation will change

00:00:43.919 --> 00:00:48.959
the project hours consumed by the project based on one hour of project runtime.

00:00:58.200 --> 00:01:03.200
For more information, visit rstudio.com or call 1-866-424-7483 to learn more about RStudio

00:01:03.200 --> 00:01:04.199
Cloud.

